        "### Fitting the Local Level Model\n",
        "\n",
        "We estimate $\\sigma_\\varepsilon^2$ and $\\sigma_\\eta^2$ by maximum likelihood\n",
        "using `statsmodels.tsa.statespace.UnobservedComponents` with\n",
        "`level='local level'`. The fitting takes a few seconds; the filter and\n",
