        "small positive autocorrelations rather than a clean AR(1) structure. The\n",
        "most natural interpretation is that the simple random-walk trend equation\n",
        "$\\mu_t = \\mu_{t-1} + \\eta_t$ is too restrictive: it forces the trend to\n",
        "change by a random step each period with no momentum of its own. A\n",
